      <title>美联储主要通胀指标将因股市上涨而提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/fed-s-main-inflation-gauge-to-get-boost-from-hot-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周五公布的数据，美联储的主要通胀指标将受到去年年底美国股市上涨的提振。]]></description>
